messages.speech: Yes. Actually, I like Japan the most because you get everything. You get lots of beautiful nature, so, you can go hiking. You can go see beautiful beaches. You can go to really nice islands, but also Japan has many, many nice citiesm ,so you can go to Tokyo, Osaka, Fukuoka and the cities have lots to do. There's good shopping, great restaurants. It's easy to travel in Japan by train and bus, so, it's really nice.
